! *		    Now restore all the flags and exit			!
! --------------------------------------------------------------------- !

]S QSEU ]S QSET ]S QSEV ]S QSES ]S	! Restore all the flags we	!
QSEH ]S QSED ]S QS^X ]S			! saved at the start		!

